data.text:
Ohio MARCS-IP: Multi-Agency Radio Communications

Project 25 Phase IWashington Co Sheriff and Marietta PD use this trunked system for communications. Their communications are encrypted and cannot be monitored by any scanner. American Electric Power (Eastern US)

EDACS Networked StandardAEP operations in the area can be found on this trunked system.
